    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chopped potato is slightly brown, remove from the oven, then add the <strong>ciabatta slices</strong> to the other side of the baking tray[s] with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and top with the <strong>grated cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for a further 4-5 min or until the cheese is melted and golden – these are your <strong>cheesy ciabatta slices</strong></p>",
