    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a separate, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-low heat</p><p>Once hot, crack your <strong>egg[s]</strong> into the pan, then cover with a lid and cook for 2-3 min or until done to your liking</p><p>Season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Tip: Give your eggs a little shake before you crack for perfectly centred yolks!</p>",
