    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>'Nduja pepper sauce </strong>with the <strong>crispy potatoes </strong>and <strong>cheesy ciabatta slices</strong> to the side</p><p>Top with the <strong>fried eggs </strong>and garnish with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped basil</strong> – this is your<strong> Italian-style brunch with spicy 'Nduja eggs</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
